---
title: One-Pot Mexican Pork Stew with Tortilla Chips
description: Packed with hearty and delicious pork and veggies, this Mexican stew is the perfect remedy to a long work week. Crushed tortilla chips and a dollop of sour cream offer a pop of flavour, perfect for finishing off this stew.
